              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer206348189649820967">This is a very thought provoking book asking each Christian to take a look at their lifestyle and ask themselves are they living the American dream or the radical Christian life. This book gave me a lot of questions to ponder and some challenges to seriously pray about.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

